<h2>How to Choose</h2>
<p><strong>Need the best quality?</strong> Midjourney is still king for artistic and photorealistic output. Nothing beats it for pure visual impact.</p>
<p><strong>Need text in your images?</strong> Ideogram is the only reliable choice for posters, ads, and social media graphics with legible text.</p>
<p><strong>Need vector graphics?</strong> Recraft is unique in generating real SVG files — ideal for logos, icons, and branding materials.</p>
<p><strong>On a budget?</strong> Stable Diffusion is completely free and runs on your own hardware. DALL-E 3 is also excellent value if you already have ChatGPT Plus.</p>
<p><strong>Building a game?</strong> Leonardo AI's specialized asset generation pipeline is unmatched for game development workflows.</p>

<h2>How We Test</h2>
<p>Each tool was evaluated on: image quality, prompt adherence, speed, pricing value, ease of use, and unique capabilities (text rendering, vector output, style consistency). Ratings reflect real-world testing across multiple scenarios from photorealistic portraits to typography-heavy designs.</p>
